Hello nfoscarini,

Each record in a compressed [w]arc is individually gzipped. A series of gzipped chunks concatenated together is itself a valid gzipped file. Perhaps the C# GZipStream doesn&#39;t realize that. I would try reading through the [w]arc iteratively by opening a new GZipStream at the offset where the last one left off.

